   uses-permission android:name= android.permission.WAKE_LOCK  /   There are also a few necessary meta-data tags that also need to be added:  meta-data android:name= com.google.android.gms.version 
    android:value= @integer/google_play_services_version  /  meta-data
    android:name= com.google.android.gms.analytics.globalConfigResource 
    android:resource= @xml/global_tracker  /   Edit the meta-data files  In the step above a file named  global_tracker.xml  was specified. This file must be placed in  proj.android/res/values/ . This file needs to contain required settings. The contents of this file could be something like this:  ?xml version= 1.0  encoding= utf-8 ?  resources 
