     string name= ga_logLevel verbose /string  /resources   Edit  Android.mk  Edit  proj.android/jni/Android.mk  to:  Add additional requirements to  LOCAL_WHOLE_STATIC_LIBRARIES :  LOCAL_WHOLE_STATIC_LIBRARIES += PluginGoogleAnalytics
