$(call import-module, ./pluginvungle)  This means that your ordering should look similar to this:  $(call import-add-path,$(LOCAL_PATH))
$(call import-module, ./sdkbox)
$(call import-module, ./pluginvungle)  Note:  It is important to make sure these statements are above the existing  $(call import-module,./prebuilt-mk)  statement, if you are using the pre-built libraries.  Modify  Application.mk  (Cocos2d-x v3.0 to v3.2 only)  Edit  proj.android/jni/Application.mk  to make sure  APP_STL  is defined
